						<summary>

						<p>On the north base of the Karivaradarāja-perumāḷ temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vīrachōḷadēva: Year 20 = 1202-03 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This incomplete and damaged inscription refers to several flower-gardens in Kumaraṅgabhīma-chaturvēdimaṅgalam, named after Adhirādhirājaṉ, Śaḍagōpan, Dēvakī-putraṉ, etc.</p>						

